short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find primary school in catchment of RE address

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Simple plugin to get the primary school within the catchment of the given address and the marketing price guide of the property. 

Usage-
Search for a listing on realestate.com.au, open any listing in a new tab, the primary school along with the marketing price range will be shown below the address of the listing.In case you open the listing on the same tab, please refresh the browser. 

Update:
